  "detailed_description": "'Stalked\" is a short first person psychological Horror game, where you play as Sarah Garrett, An investigative journalist being stalked in the middle of the night.<br><br>Gameplay:<br><br>∎Creepy Neighborhood with tension build-up<br>∎No random Jumpscares<br>∎Cardboard cutouts and more hilarious things<br>∎Music that will make your ears bleed with immersion /Voice Acting<br>∎Multiple Endings / Leaving Options<br><br><u>Avg playtime maybe between 1 hour and more depending on pace and how much you explore.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513660/extras/0b1f0c718cbda64f28caf89434f4dc9f.poster.avif?t=1665962577\" width=640 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513660/extras/0b1f0c718cbda64f28caf89434f4dc9f.webm?t=1665962577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513660/extras/0b1f0c718cbda64f28caf89434f4dc9f.mp4?t=1665962577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
